"""
Gviven the lengths of the three sides of a triangle. Retun the area of
 the triangle rounded to 2 decimal poinst if the three sides form a valid triangle. 
Otherwise return -1
Three sides make a valid triangle when the sum of any two sides is greater 
than the third side.
